---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-vnn-charcoal text-white mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-vnn-blue rounded flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold font-serif">V</span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold">Valyrian News Network</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
          AI-synthesized, context-rich news analysis with full transparency.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-4 text-white">Links</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white no-underline">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white no-underline">About Our Methodology</a></li>
          <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white no-underline">RSS Feed</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-4 text-white">Valyrian Tech</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
          VNN is a project of Valyrian Tech, powered by the SERENDIPITY AGI framework.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="border-t border-gray-700 mt-8 pt-8 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} Valyrian Tech. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Articles are synthesized by AI systems. 
        <a href="/about" class="text-vnn-blue hover:underline">Learn about our methodology</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
